How to Build the Docs
(a continuation of "Documentation Plan" on the now-inaccessible wiki)

Install 'xmlto' and run:

    xmlto -v html-nochunks UDP.xml

If you get this error:

I/O error : Attempt to load network entity
http://docbook.org/xml/4.3/ent/iso-num.ent
/home/jeff/p2p/sumi/doc/tmp/UDP.xml:7: warning: failed to load external entity
"http://docbook.org/xml/4.3/ent/iso-num.ent"

then either comment out -nonet in `which xmlto`, or install docbook.

UDP.xml (came from UDP For Anonymity.xml) had to be modified to be a complete
DocBook file. Need to work on wt2db. See wt2db-missing.

